We're not what you think.

00:35.802 --> 00:38.373
We're nice and normal and weird, too,

00:38.438 --> 00:40.847
and we all go to a school together and...

00:41.708 --> 00:45.087
Wait. Let me start from the beginning.

00:46.279 --> 00:49.155
At first, it was just
lonely little me and my dad,

00:49.215 --> 00:52.219
flapping around in our very big, old house.

00:55.054 --> 00:57.056
But then I met Frankie.

00:59.559 --> 01:01.770
And then I met Clawdeen.

01:04.096 --> 01:08.102
And together, we decided
to turn our house into a school.

01:08.168 --> 01:09.609
Monster High!

01:09.669 --> 01:12.650
A place where every monster is welcome.

01:14.040 --> 01:18.617
My dad gave me an ancient monster
transporter called a Mapalogue.

01:21.014 --> 01:24.928
We used it to rescue monsters
from all over the world.

01:28.021 --> 01:30.997
I've made so many fangtastic new friends,

01:31.057 --> 01:34.231
and now Monster High is filled with students.

01:37.230 --> 01:39.506
And you're welcome to join us, too.

01:40.099 --> 01:42.041
All you have to do is...

01:42.101 --> 01:44.172
Draculaura, official Mapalogue emergency!

01:44.237 --> 01:46.148
- We found another ghoul!
- Right.

01:47.106 --> 01:48.380
Come along.

01:48.441 --> 01:50.921
Silvi exto monstrum!

02:21.541 --> 02:23.612
- Come on! Did you see it?
- It's over there.

02:50.336 --> 02:52.316
- Where did it go?
- Have you seen it?

02:54.340 --> 02:55.682
Maybe it climbed the fence?

02:55.742 --> 02:58.120
Nah, wolves can't climb.
Let's check the other side.

03:11.224 --> 03:16.171
Hi! We're your official welcoming committee
and we would just like to say... Huh?

03:17.330 --> 03:18.536
Where is she?

03:18.598 --> 03:19.804
Down here!

03:21.567 --> 03:24.673
Help me, please.
They've got the place surrounded.

03:24.737 --> 03:26.145
- Did you hear that?
- Huh?

03:26.205 --> 03:28.879
- What's going on?
- It sounded electrical?

03:28.941 --> 03:31.182
- So rude!
- I think we'd better do something.

03:31.244 --> 03:34.687
Of course. But will we still
have time for a bite before...

03:34.747 --> 03:37.688
- There! In the alley. Come on!
- Oh? Where did it go?

03:37.750 --> 03:39.286
Ghouls, let's move.

03:46.326 --> 03:49.165
- Whoa. Hey! Is there a blackout?
- What's going on?

03:52.481 --> 03:54.428
What was that?

04:00.039 --> 04:01.450
I see something!

04:06.512 --> 04:08.048
- There!
- Don't let it get away.

04:08.114 --> 04:09.115
Go, go, go, go!

04:13.452 --> 04:14.553
Thank you.

04:14.721 --> 04:16.325
- No worries.
- No problem.

04:16.389 --> 04:17.390
Our pleasure.

04:17.857 --> 04:18.858
Happy to help.

04:21.194 --> 04:22.571
It's what we do.

04:24.230 --> 04:25.470
Who are you?

04:26.565 --> 04:30.238
Hi, we're your official welcoming committee,
and we would just like to say...

04:30.303 --> 04:31.304
Uh...

04:31.371 --> 04:35.012
Ghouls, I think the Normies
figured out they've been tricked.

04:35.074 --> 04:36.075
Time to go.

04:40.113 --> 04:43.390
Don't worry. We're monsters, too.
Obviously. Come on.

04:56.195 --> 05:00.106
Okay. So now, as your
official welcoming committee,

05:00.166 --> 05:02.305
we would just like to say...

05:02.368 --> 05:04.245
Welcome to Monster High!

05:46.112 --> 05:49.389
Frankie is really amped up
about this science project, huh?

05:49.449 --> 05:50.951
Have you seen it? It's, uh...

05:51.017 --> 05:54.360
It's, uh, amazing! Isn't it?

05:54.420 --> 05:57.128
You have no idea what it is, do you?

05:57.190 --> 05:59.295
- Nope.
- Glad I'm not the only one.

05:59.358 --> 06:01.235
What is that thing, anyway?

06:03.529 --> 06:05.702
It's an ultra-high-density
direct current capacitator

06:05.765 --> 06:07.676
for storing high levels of electric energy.

06:09.101 --> 06:10.102
Neat.

06:10.169 --> 06:11.876
It's like a super battery.

06:11.938 --> 06:15.575
I'm trying to put
all that electricity into this.

06:15.641 --> 06:18.551
Imagine only having to charge
your phone once a year!

06:18.611 --> 06:22.115
Oh! And for the Normies,
electricity is everything.

06:22.181 --> 06:25.525
This device is really going to change
their world for the better.

06:25.585 --> 06:27.223
- Amazing!
- Fascinating.

06:27.286 --> 06:29.698
