06:58.684 --> 07:00.186
Hmm.

07:05.825 --> 07:07.736
You wanna go see Ari?
I hear she's performing right now.

07:08.294 --> 07:11.204
Isn't it great?
Just look at all these monsters.

07:11.264 --> 07:15.041
Together, under one roof,
making friends with each other.

07:24.110 --> 07:25.555
Oh, yeah!

07:26.345 --> 07:27.983
Looking good.

07:36.022 --> 07:38.831
And it looks like the new
ghoul even made a friend.

07:38.891 --> 07:41.895
