Whoa!

58:53.363 --> 58:54.842
Frankie!

58:55.531 --> 58:56.973
All right, ghoul!

58:57.033 --> 58:58.341
- Frankie!
- You are back!

58:58.401 --> 58:59.778
You're okay!

59:00.303 --> 59:03.182
Aw. Thanks to Znap and you ghouls!

59:05.975 --> 59:08.854
- And you were right, Twyla.
- Oh. Um...

59:09.245 --> 59:11.350
I can't do everything on my own.

59:11.781 --> 59:13.256
Znap!

59:14.117 --> 59:15.858
Znap, Znap, Znap.

59:15.918 --> 59:17.090
You're right, Znap!

59:17.153 --> 59:19.656
With Moanica and the Zomboys
out scaring all the Normies,

59:19.722 --> 59:21.793
there's no way they'll ever trust us.

59:21.858 --> 59:23.098
Unless we do something.

59:23.159 --> 59:26.536
Moanica has hundreds of Zomboys
out scaring those Normies.

59:26.596 --> 59:28.473
It'd take an army to stop them!

59:29.132 --> 59:31.772
Znap! Znap! Znap!

59:38.041 --> 59:39.349
It's...

59:39.409 --> 59:41.184
It's beautiful.

59:50.386 --> 59:51.956
So proud.

01:00:08.871 --> 01:00:10.612
Hey. Ghouls.

01:00:10.673 --> 01:00:13.116
Think you could turn the outfits down a bit?

01:00:13.176 --> 01:00:17.587
They're kinda messing up the whole dark
and scary mood we've got going here.

01:00:17.647 --> 01:00:19.217
